                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="4v" to="281v">4v-281v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="apodous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA">قران</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#4v">-4v</locus>بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم / سبحان الذي اسرى بعده ليلا من المسجد الحرام الى المسجد الأقصى </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#281v">-281v</locus>فانذرتكم نارا تلظى لا يصلاها الا الاشقى الذي</explicit>
                     <note>Part contains Quran section 17:01 - 92:16.
Text is in red double frame. Sura titles are marked in red with information on number of verses. 
 
There are several interruptions in the text: 
123v begins with words 23 - 28 of 33:35 which constitutes a direct continuation of text on 123r. Hereafter however the text jumps to word 15 of 24:26 continuing until word 3 of 24:30 at the bottom of the page. This section has subsequently been crossed out.
The catch word on 123v من indicates that the scribe intended to continue from 24:30 on the following page. But before doing so he must have realized his mistake. 
From the top of 124r the text returns to word 23 of 33:35. 

Folio 278 should have been placed between folios 279 and 280. Catchwords indicate that this was the scribes intention. </note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="282r" to="283v">282r-283v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="apodous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA">قران</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#282r">-282r</locus>منهم معرة بغير علم ليدخل الله في رحمته من يشأ لو تزيلوا لعذبنا الذين كفروا منهم عذابا أليما</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#283v">-283v</locus>وعد الله الذين امنوا وعملوا الصالحات منهم</explicit>
                     <note>Begins at word 23 of Qur'an 48:25 and ands at word 52 of Qur'an 48:29.
Written in different hand than 4v - 281v. 
Catch word مغفره on 283v indicates continuation.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
